WEBVTT

00:04:58.063 --> 00:05:02.723
to rape, threaten, intimidate
and brutalize those civilians

00:05:02.747 --> 00:05:04.151
at every turn.

00:05:04.937 --> 00:05:06.088
How cheap?

00:05:06.112 --> 00:05:07.728
Well, in some parts of the world,

00:05:07.752 --> 00:05:12.150
you can buy an AK-47
for as little as 10 dollars.

00:05:12.174 --> 00:05:15.030
In many places in which I have worked,

00:05:15.621 --> 00:05:20.118
it is easier to get access
to an automatic rifle

00:05:20.142 --> 00:05:24.263
than it is to get access
to clean drinking water.

00:05:25.040 --> 00:05:26.636
And so now the important part:

00:05:27.699 --> 00:05:30.818
Can anything be done about this?